org.apache.felix.ipojo.handlers.dependency

Class ServiceList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.handlers.dependency.ServiceList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable, Collection, List

    public class ServiceList
extends Object
implements List
    Maintains a list of service object. This collection wrap the dependency to be accessible from a Collection or a List, that can be passed to helper objects (Collaborators).

    The Collection.iterator() method returns an Iterator iterating on a cached copy of available service objects. In the case that there are no available services, the policies act as follows:

    • 'null' returns a null iterator
    • 'nullable' and default-implementation returns an iterator iterating on one object (the nullable or default-implementation object
    • 'empty' returns an empty iterator.
    Because of FELIX-4717, this class does not implement Set.
    Author:
    Felix Project Team
